If you're at 1024x768 resolution, try these setting for  hitsmode. You'll want to turn all misses off, as those don't get put in the boxes. This setting gets you 3 small boxes that pop up over your chat box. They only appear when there is activity in them.<br>
<br>
/hitsmode my m3 190 590 5 0 1 200 0<br>
/hitsmode me m3 400 590 5 0 1 200 0<br>
/hitsmode other m3 610 590 5 0 1 210 0 <br>
<br>
Now if you want them up all the time, use these commands. <br>
<br>
/hitsmode my m3 190 590 5 0 1 200 1<br>
/hitsmode me m3 400 590 5 0 1 200 1<br>
/hitsmode other m3 610 590 5 0 1 210 1 <br>
<br>
